OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778583777
OL,3,CLabour MP Catherine West threatens to
OL,4,Coust Starmer
OL,6,FThe Cabinet should unite around a
OL,7,Fcandidate to replace Sir Keir Starmer
OL,8,Fto take the fight to Nigel Farage and
OL,9,FReform UK, Labour MP Catherine West
OL,10,Fhas said.
OL,12,FThe MP for Hornsey and Friern Barnet
OL,13,Fvowed to launch a leadership campaign
OL,14,Funless Sir Keir is ousted by his
OL,15,FCabinet, also suggested Andy Burnham
OL,16,Fshould be given a seat in the Lords.
OL,18,FSpeaking in North London on Saturday
OL,19,Fnight, she explained the "electoral
OL,20,Fcrisis" Labour now faces and her plans
OL,21,Ffor change.
OL,26,@{D@ZOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778583777
OL,3,CLabour MP Catherine West threatens to
OL,4,Coust Starmer
OL,6,FMs West said:
OL,8,F"What I'd really like to see is not a
OL,9,Fleadership election, but for them to
OL,10,Fcome together and appoint somebody
OL,11,Famongst them who can lead us and give
OL,12,Fus a vision of how we're going to
OL,13,Fdefeat Nigel Farage and the right wing
OL,14,Fin the coming general election, which
OL,15,Fcould be as soon as possible."
OL,17,FFor Ms West to challenge Sir Keir she
OL,18,Fwould need the backing of 20% of
OL,19,FLabour's 403 MPs ` a total of 81.
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778583777
OL,3,CLabour MP Catherine West threatens to
OL,4,Coust Starmer
OL,6,FShe believes this is possible by
OL,7,Fcalling on her colleagues on Monday.
OL,9,FThe shake-up comes after the fallout
OL,10,Fof Labour's election results, with
OL,11,Fmany MPs calling for Sir Keir to go
OL,12,Fand the party losing control of
OL,13,Fseveral councils.
OL,15,FMr Burnham, Labour Mayor of
OL,16,FManchester, has been widely touted as
OL,17,Fa candidate to face Sir Keir in a
OL,18,Fleadership challenge.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778583777
OL,3,CLabour MP Catherine West threatens to
OL,4,Coust Starmer
OL,6,FWhen asked if Ms West's new decision
OL,7,Fto challenge Sir Keir is to prevent Mr
OL,8,FBurnham getting a chance, she said
OL,9,F"not at all".
OL,11,FMs West said:
OL,13,F"Not at all. I think Andy should be
OL,14,Fpart of the leadership team, and I
OL,15,Fwould expect that any leader will want
OL,16,Fto appoint Andy, perhaps, to the House
OL,17,Fof Lords, because you could be a
OL,18,Fminister in the House of Lords, and he
OL,19,Fwould make a fantastic contribution.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@LO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778583777
OL,3,CLabour MP Catherine West threatens to
OL,4,Coust Starmer
OL,6,F"Whether he can necessarily be the
OL,7,Fprime minister from the House of
OL,8,FLords, that would be very unusual."
OL,10,FIn a bid to salvage support, Sir Keir
OL,11,Fgave advisory roles to Labour grandees
OL,12,FGordon Brown and Baroness Harriet
OL,13,FHarman on Saturday.
OL,15,FDespite this, Ms West said the Cabinet
OL,16,Fneeds to lock "itself in a room
OL,17,Ftonight" and come up with a plan to
OL,18,Fsave Labour. She said:
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@cO]xD@OOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778583777
OL,3,CLabour MP Catherine West threatens to
OL,4,Coust Starmer
OL,6,F"What I'd like to see is the Cabinet
OL,7,Flocking itself in a room tonight and
OL,8,Fcoming up with a plan to respond to
OL,9,Fwhat was the worst election result for
OL,10,Fthe Labour Party that I can remember,
OL,11,Fand I've been in public life since
OL,12,F2001.
OL,14,F"This is what we would describe as an
OL,15,Felectoral emergency and sadly, the
OL,16,FCabinet have not come out strongly to
OL,17,Flead us, to tell us what's coming
OL,18,Fnext."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778583777
OL,3,CLabour MP Catherine West threatens to
OL,4,Coust Starmer
OL,6,FMs West went on to say that from on
OL,7,FSunday and Monday she will be "doing
OL,8,Fsome more challenging".
OL,10,F"I am doing some more challenging the
OL,11,Fcurrent way that we're approaching
OL,12,Fthis crisis, and I hope that this will
OL,13,Fbring forward either a bit more fight
OL,14,Fon the current leader, or some
OL,15,Fleadership hopefuls, who will come
OL,16,Fforward and say, we've been challenged
OL,17,Fand this is our plan, to bring forward
OL,18,Fa change, and bring forward a change
OL,19,Fin the country, and bring forward
OL,20,Frenewed respect.
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@VO]rD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778583777
OL,3,CLabour MP Catherine West threatens to
OL,4,Coust Starmer
OL,6,F"I haven't heard what we're going to
OL,7,Fdo differently or how that's going to
OL,8,Fbe different."And that's why I want to
OL,9,Ftry and shake up the party so that
OL,10,Fthey can respond to what was an awful
OL,11,Felection result on Thursday."
OL,13,FMs West explained that she believes
OL,14,FReform UK's success in the local
OL,15,Felections is partly down to how they
OL,16,Fhave taken over "a traditional role of
OL,17,Fthe Labour Party". She continued:
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@NOUsD@]O]xD@QOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778583777
OL,3,CLabour MP Catherine West threatens to
OL,4,Coust Starmer
OL,6,F"The only way of beating Reform is for
OL,7,Fthe Labour Party to get itself
OL,8,Forganised, better funded, we need to
OL,9,Fdo more fundraising, because Nigel
OL,10,FFarage clearly has people who will
OL,11,Fjust give him #5 million.
OL,13,F"We need to understand where that
OL,14,Fmoney came from, we need to understand
OL,15,Fhow they operate."
OL,17,FAnd also, we need to look at their
OL,18,Fmethods of communication, because they
OL,19,Fclearly were able to communicate with
OL,20,Fworking people, which is a traditional
OL,21,Frole of the Labour Party."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@ROU}D@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
