OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778583777
OL,3,CLabour MP Catherine West threatens to
OL,4,Coust Starmer
OL,6,FOn Monday, Sir Keir Starmer will set
OL,7,Fout a "fresh direction" as he battles
OL,8,Fto save his job in the face of a
OL,9,Fleadership challenge following
OL,10,FLabour's disastrous election results.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister, who indicated that
OL,13,Fhe hopes to remain in power until
OL,14,F2034, has a major speech on Monday as
OL,15,Fhe tries to shore up his position
OL,16,Fafter the MP Catherine West declared
OL,17,Fher intention to launch a leadership
OL,18,Fbid.
OL,26,@oD@GOUoD@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
