PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778583777
OL,3,CLabour MP Catherine West threatens to
OL,4,Coust Starmer
OL,6,FMs West said she would wait to hear
OL,7,FSir Keir's speech on Monday before
OL,8,Fbeginning the process of gathering the
OL,9,F81 MPs she would need to formally
OL,10,Ftrigger a contest.
